{"id":121123,"type":6,"name":"Bad Judge","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/1b/80/121123_b1muG.jpg","rating":{"total":6,"count":{"1":0,"2":1,"3":0,"4":0,"5":1,"6":0,"7":2,"8":2,"9":0,"10":0},"score":6.2},"summary":"没有借口，不用道歉，决不妥协。从小到大都像野孩子的Rebecca Wright知道如何给自己找乐子，但她凑巧是洛杉矶市最强硬、最受人尊敬的刑事法庭大法官之一。她以在法庭上做出反传统的行为而闻名——包括一些其他法 官想都不敢想的创意，想说就说，从不隐瞒自己的意见。但是在私人生活中，她喜欢疯狂地聚会，和自己最好的朋友Jenny在一支乐队中如痴如狂地敲大鼓。她 的生活中从来都不缺乏追求者，她的入幕之宾也换了一个又一个，但她还不想成家，直到一个八岁男孩的出现改变了一切——Rebecca将他的父母全都关了起 来，现在他需要她的帮助。他是唯一能让这个“坏法官”安静下来的人。只要有他在，Rebecca就会变得温顺，一种做母亲的感觉油然而生。","info":"<li><span>中文名: </span>坏法官</li><li><span>集数: </span>13</li><li><span>开始: </span>2014-10-02(美国)</li><li><span>类型: </span>喜剧</li><li><span>国家/地区: </span>美国</li><li><span>语言: </span>英语</li><li><span>每集长: </span>30分钟</li><li><span>imdb_id: </span>tt2769470</li>","collection":{"wish":1,"collect":5,"on_hold":1},"tags":[{"name":"美剧","count":3},{"name":"2014年","count":1},{"name":"NBC","count":1},{"name":"TV","count":1},{"name":"喜剧","count":1}],"eps":[{"id":461302,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/461302","type":0,"sort":1,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":461303,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/461303","type":0,"sort":2,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":461304,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/461304","type":0,"sort":3,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":461305,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/461305","type":0,"sort":4,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":461306,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/461306","type":0,"sort":5,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":461307,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/461307","type":0,"sort":6,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":461308,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/461308","type":0,"sort":7,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airda